metadata.name: Epiphany
metadata.description:
An epiphany is a sudden and intense realization of the inherent nature and reality of things. 

While our conscious mind perceives, the subconscious mind is always calculating with mathematical certainty. 

Through certain states of consciousness, we can sometimes perceive that which is not always readily available.

4096 x 4096 300 DPI

1/1 limited edition NFT
